WEBVTT

01:26.110 --> 01:34.990
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.450 --> 01:37.880
[Episode 19]

01:39.060 --> 01:40.210
You are still de...

01:40.259 --> 01:41.350
defending that man!

01:41.350 --> 01:43.220
I knew I caught you cheating!

01:43.400 --> 01:43.990
What did...

01:43.990 --> 01:44.920
What did you say?

01:45.000 --> 01:45.860
What cheating?

01:45.950 --> 01:47.479
Get out. All of you, get out.

01:47.479 --> 01:47.990
No, I...

01:48.090 --> 01:48.780
Don't you

01:48.780 --> 01:49.400
slander her here!

01:49.400 --> 01:49.840
No...

01:49.870 --> 01:51.840
Zhuang Zhuang rejected you long ago!

01:51.840 --> 01:53.240
Who she is with now

01:53.850 --> 01:55.500
is none of your business at all!

01:55.500 --> 01:56.780
Please calm down.

01:56.840 --> 01:57.770
You... You!

01:58.259 --> 01:59.710
Look how angry you made her.

01:59.710 --> 02:00.710
You are really...

02:00.790 --> 02:02.740
Let's talk things out nicely.

02:02.950 --> 02:04.350
What was the rush? You...

02:04.510 --> 02:05.260
Didn't you just say

02:05.260 --> 02:05.810
we should

02:05.810 --> 02:07.260
stay out of the kids' business?

02:07.260 --> 02:08.560
Zhuang Zhuang, look,

02:08.780 --> 02:09.530
it's the first day

02:09.530 --> 02:10.310
of the New Year,

02:10.310 --> 02:11.680
and we brought all these gifts

02:11.680 --> 02:12.520
to convey our New Year greetings.

02:12.520 --> 02:13.250
We are totally sincere.

02:13.250 --> 02:13.910
Take them away.

02:13.910 --> 02:14.470
We want to...

02:14.470 --> 02:15.860
-Take them all away!
-We can't do that!

02:15.860 --> 02:17.340
We brought these gifts especially for you.

02:17.340 --> 02:18.210
You should know that

02:18.210 --> 02:19.840
with our family's conditions,

02:19.840 --> 02:21.560
if our son were in Wenzhou,

02:21.840 --> 02:23.560
plenty of girls would like him.

02:23.560 --> 02:25.220
Y-You should just be with him.

02:25.240 --> 02:26.150
Auntie,

02:26.190 --> 02:27.300
you can't

02:27.300 --> 02:28.340
force feelings.

02:28.340 --> 02:29.800
I just like Zhuang Zhuang!

02:29.910 --> 02:31.300
I don't like you!

02:34.190 --> 02:34.590
You...

02:35.060 --> 02:36.120
What are you doing,

02:36.130 --> 02:36.970
Ye?

02:37.360 --> 02:38.150
It's the New Year.

02:38.150 --> 02:38.800
Why are you

02:38.800 --> 02:39.930
yelling in our house?

02:39.930 --> 02:40.750
We are not.

02:40.800 --> 02:42.079
We came to pay you a new year visit

02:42.079 --> 02:43.740
with all these gifts!

02:44.090 --> 02:45.690
Besides being filthy rich,

02:45.710 --> 02:46.310
what else do you have?

02:46.310 --> 02:48.510
My daughter doesn't like him. Get lost!

02:48.710 --> 02:49.620
Ye.

02:51.930 --> 02:53.380
How can you say that?

02:53.870 --> 02:55.230
That's too harsh.

02:55.750 --> 02:56.340
Let's go.

02:57.000 --> 02:57.370
Come on!

02:57.370 --> 02:57.700
Wait.

02:57.740 --> 02:58.900
Mom, why are we leaving?

02:58.900 --> 03:00.030
I seriously

03:00.030 --> 03:00.960
can't believe you.

03:00.960 --> 03:02.460
Trust me, you'll regret this!

03:02.460 --> 03:04.430
-Take your red packet. Take your money!
-No, you can have it!

03:04.430 --> 03:05.020
Take them away!

03:05.020 --> 03:05.880
You can have it!

03:06.180 --> 03:07.040
No, Mom, why...

03:07.500 --> 03:08.840
W-Why are we leaving?

03:09.460 --> 03:10.750
I haven't eaten the snacks yet,

03:10.750 --> 03:12.580
and the red packet
is still on the table, Mom.

03:12.580 --> 03:13.440
I'm sorry, Mom.

03:14.190 --> 03:15.400
I'm sorry, Mr. Ye.

03:18.120 --> 03:18.970
Don't be mad.

03:18.990 --> 03:20.880
Why didn't you say anything?

03:21.680 --> 03:23.140
I didn't want you to worry.

03:24.090 --> 03:25.290
The money and things,

03:25.340 --> 03:26.670
I'll return them later.

03:32.579 --> 03:35.040
Why are you making me
go to some dinner again?

03:36.060 --> 03:37.000
No matter whom I meet,

03:37.000 --> 03:38.079
they all say the same stuff.

03:38.079 --> 03:39.079
What's the point?

03:41.190 --> 03:42.670
This one is different.

03:42.910 --> 03:43.880
This guy

03:43.940 --> 03:46.450
is the cousin of your aunt's classmate.

03:46.630 --> 03:48.829
You went to the same elementary school.

03:49.970 --> 03:52.340
I was thinking you should
leave a few days later

03:52.340 --> 03:53.910
and meet a few more boys.

03:54.470 --> 03:56.400
What if there's someone suitable?

03:56.410 --> 03:57.540
That would be great.

03:57.690 --> 03:59.810
If he has some connections in Beijing,

03:59.810 --> 04:01.700
he could even help you out.

04:01.840 --> 04:03.300
To hell with connections.

04:04.210 --> 04:05.330
Everyone in Beijing says

04:05.330 --> 04:06.520
they have connections.

04:06.520 --> 04:07.960
But how many are actually of help?

04:07.960 --> 04:09.220
This one's different.

04:09.410 --> 04:11.360
He has a family business.

04:11.690 --> 04:13.550
I don't know exactly what he does.

04:14.190 --> 04:16.140
I just know he's rich.

04:17.370 --> 04:19.450
You went to the same elementary school.

04:19.450 --> 04:21.130
He's just 6 years older than you.

04:21.130 --> 04:22.040
But look at him.

04:22.180 --> 04:23.930
He's already a big boss now.

04:24.830 --> 04:26.720
If a brick falls in Beijing,

04:27.300 --> 04:28.960
it could hit dozens of bosses.

04:41.500 --> 04:41.960
Ranran.

04:42.680 --> 04:44.310
Be honest with me.

04:45.190 --> 04:46.260
Is there

04:46.630 --> 04:49.480
someone you like in Beijing?

04:50.480 --> 04:51.340
Is he a big boss?

04:52.800 --> 04:53.630
A rich one?

04:55.430 --> 04:56.070
No.

05:05.270 --> 05:06.630
Is it wrong for a mother

05:06.930 --> 05:08.870
to worry about her daughter?

05:10.270 --> 05:11.250
All these years,

05:11.660 --> 05:12.370
raising you

05:12.370 --> 05:13.700
and your brother alone,

05:13.740 --> 05:15.000
has it been easy for me?

05:16.620 --> 05:18.950
I gave birth to such a beautiful daughter,

05:19.270 --> 05:21.630
but it's completely useless now.

05:22.560 --> 05:23.510
Ranran,

05:23.560 --> 05:25.740
can you put my mind at ease?

05:26.070 --> 05:27.620
I just want you

05:27.620 --> 05:29.330
to find a reliable family

05:29.330 --> 05:30.800
and get married soon.

05:32.980 --> 05:34.220
You keep making me meet these guys

05:34.220 --> 05:35.659
who are so out of touch with reality.

05:35.659 --> 05:37.370
Where am I supposed to
find a reliable man?

05:37.370 --> 05:39.330
This one is different!

05:39.830 --> 05:41.600
Didn't I say

05:41.630 --> 05:43.180
he is a boss?

05:43.250 --> 05:45.600
He's the cousin of your aunt's classmate.

05:45.870 --> 05:46.800
Besides,

05:46.980 --> 05:48.040
I'll go with you.

05:48.270 --> 05:50.000
He can't take advantage of you!

05:53.930 --> 05:54.390
Fine.

05:55.190 --> 05:56.290
Um, Dad,

05:56.330 --> 05:58.390
is there anything you need help with?

05:58.390 --> 05:58.980
Help?

06:02.330 --> 06:03.460
What can you even do?

06:04.740 --> 06:06.660
Fine, I can't do anything.

06:07.680 --> 06:08.410
I have to say,

06:09.270 --> 06:10.130
the pork knuckle you bought

06:10.130 --> 06:10.990
is pretty good.

06:11.690 --> 06:13.380
Well, Shengli.

06:13.660 --> 06:14.520
Shengli, look.

06:15.010 --> 06:15.870
I was wondering

06:16.430 --> 06:17.330
how you knew

06:17.330 --> 06:18.660
I love all these pastries!

06:18.660 --> 06:19.740
There's a bit of everything.

06:19.740 --> 06:20.720
It's so nice.

06:20.800 --> 06:21.710
Of course.

06:21.740 --> 06:22.800
This is what my g...

06:27.160 --> 06:28.040
A friend of mine

06:28.040 --> 06:29.970
carefully picked them out with me.

06:30.810 --> 06:31.720
A girlfriend?

06:37.180 --> 06:38.060
No, no.

06:38.060 --> 06:39.680
Hey, what does she look like?

06:39.720 --> 06:40.690
What does she do?

06:40.690 --> 06:41.540
Tell me about it.

06:41.540 --> 06:42.300
No, Mom.

06:42.370 --> 06:43.970
W-We are not there yet.

06:44.100 --> 06:44.720
U-Um...

06:44.770 --> 06:46.900
I'm sleepy. I-I'm going back to sleep.

06:53.220 --> 06:54.000
Did you hear that?

06:54.000 --> 06:55.720
Your son is seeing someone.

06:56.100 --> 06:56.960
So what if he is?

06:57.830 --> 06:59.230
He got his looks from you.

06:59.330 --> 07:00.390
Isn't it expected?

07:02.280 --> 07:03.620
He just didn't tell us

07:03.980 --> 07:05.300
what the girl does.

07:05.450 --> 07:07.250
He didn't even show us a picture.

07:07.810 --> 07:08.470
Go find out.

07:09.720 --> 07:10.240
Me?

07:12.720 --> 07:14.050
Aren't you curious too?

07:14.740 --> 07:15.860
Don't act like you don't care.

07:15.860 --> 07:16.480
I'm not going.

07:16.480 --> 07:17.540
Look at you. You...

07:23.040 --> 07:23.930
Lili, let's go.

07:25.540 --> 07:26.120
Coming.

07:26.680 --> 07:28.360
I haven't been to
the newly opened mall either.

07:28.360 --> 07:29.630
They say it has everything,

07:29.630 --> 07:30.770
with discounts for the New Year.

07:30.770 --> 07:32.370
Let's see what we can buy for you.

07:32.370 --> 07:34.300
No need. Let's just look around.

07:34.320 --> 07:35.580
Just hurry up. Come on.

07:36.240 --> 07:37.630
You go first, and I'll lock the door.

07:37.630 --> 07:39.020
You're just missing a pocketbook.

07:39.020 --> 07:40.280
I'll buy you one later.

07:40.330 --> 07:41.530
What's a pocketbook?

07:41.659 --> 07:42.420
It's a bag.

07:43.510 --> 07:45.540
That's what you call it there?

07:45.570 --> 07:48.570
Well, isn't a bag used to hold your stuff
like a pocket?

08:16.620 --> 08:18.200
Hello? Hey, Cui.

08:19.660 --> 08:20.790
Only you can help me.

08:22.000 --> 08:22.690
Ranran,

08:22.740 --> 08:24.400
you think too highly of me.

08:24.750 --> 08:25.950
I'm not that capable.

08:26.370 --> 08:26.890
I can't

08:26.890 --> 08:28.220
get the tickets either.

08:29.220 --> 08:31.920
It's OK. Happy New Year.

08:37.360 --> 08:38.960
I'm not up to any tricks!

08:39.120 --> 08:40.750
I'm just being sincere.

08:40.940 --> 08:42.960
Fine. Thank you for your sincerity.

08:43.909 --> 08:45.710
Say hello to your parents for me.

08:46.770 --> 08:48.220
Does your mom like

08:48.370 --> 08:49.430
the jujube pastry?

08:49.720 --> 08:50.170
Or I could

08:50.170 --> 08:51.700
ask Little Northeasterner
to send some more.

08:51.700 --> 08:52.270
No need.

08:52.600 --> 08:54.400
We'll get diabetes at this rate.

08:57.750 --> 08:59.370
Are you planning to go back to Beijing

08:59.370 --> 09:00.970
after the Lantern Festival?

09:01.360 --> 09:03.220
I haven't decided yet. You?

09:03.790 --> 09:05.590
I probably have to go back early.

09:05.860 --> 09:07.860
I guess I'll have to leave on the 5th.

09:08.510 --> 09:10.830
You... You're going back on the 5th?

09:11.580 --> 09:13.110
Do you have something to do?

09:13.770 --> 09:15.480
-First, I really need to
-Is he in a hurry to leave?

09:15.480 --> 09:17.140
prepare for the competition.

09:18.670 --> 09:19.480
And second...

09:22.630 --> 09:23.860
Let's talk about it later

09:23.860 --> 09:25.100
when you get to Beijing.

09:25.100 --> 09:25.880
Sure.

09:26.440 --> 09:28.890
I guess the earliest I can go is

09:29.240 --> 09:30.270
the 8th or 9th.

09:30.270 --> 09:30.840
OK.

09:31.900 --> 09:33.370
I'll tell you when I decide.

09:33.370 --> 09:34.230
Bring it to him.

09:34.250 --> 09:35.720
See you in Beijing then.

09:36.250 --> 09:39.650
-OK, see you in Beijing.
-Go hear what they're talking about.

09:42.180 --> 09:43.090
Hurry up.

09:45.010 --> 09:46.270
The 5th...

09:46.390 --> 09:48.680
Son, I got some water for you.

09:49.100 --> 09:51.630
You must be thirsty
after talking for so long.

09:52.550 --> 09:53.120
Son,

09:53.440 --> 09:55.840
were you on the phone
with your girlfriend?

09:56.000 --> 09:57.500
How many times must I tell you

09:57.500 --> 09:58.900
she's not my girlfriend?

09:59.080 --> 10:00.300
We're just friends.

10:00.370 --> 10:01.450
OK, OK, friends.

10:01.550 --> 10:02.510
Yes, I got it.

10:03.050 --> 10:04.740
Friendship is the first step.

10:04.860 --> 10:05.750
Take one more step,

10:05.750 --> 10:07.350
and you'll be dating, right?

10:08.720 --> 10:10.630
What's the girl like?

10:12.270 --> 10:13.000
Pretty good.

10:13.700 --> 10:14.700
Pretty good, huh?

10:15.620 --> 10:17.250
Do you have a picture or something?

10:17.250 --> 10:18.380
Let me check her out.

10:19.140 --> 10:20.340
I knew you'd ask me

10:20.500 --> 10:21.630
once I talked to her

10:22.100 --> 10:22.890
on the phone.

10:24.620 --> 10:25.550
There really is.

10:27.480 --> 10:29.740
She is so pretty.

10:31.670 --> 10:32.550
So pretty.

10:33.200 --> 10:34.240
Where is she from?

10:34.240 --> 10:34.970
Wenzhou.

10:35.200 --> 10:36.410
Her name is Zhuang Zhuang.

10:36.410 --> 10:37.210
Z-Zhuang?

10:37.500 --> 10:38.700
What's her full name?

10:38.700 --> 10:40.430
Zhuang Zhuang's her full name.

10:40.600 --> 10:41.440
Zhuang Zhuang is her full name?

10:41.440 --> 10:42.570
Yes, Zhuang Zhuang.

10:43.030 --> 10:43.890
Zhuang Zhuang.

10:45.000 --> 10:46.170
What does she do?

10:46.240 --> 10:48.240
She's studying singing in Beijing.

10:48.390 --> 10:50.220
Folk songs.
She's preparing to join an ensemble.

10:50.220 --> 10:51.170
Really?

10:53.010 --> 10:54.120
That's great.

10:55.390 --> 10:56.250
Let me tell you,

10:56.360 --> 10:58.210
I really like this girl.

10:58.890 --> 10:59.960
Be serious about it.

10:59.960 --> 11:01.890
Give it your best shot, you hear me?

11:02.250 --> 11:03.370
Alright, got it.

11:03.600 --> 11:04.610
I'll try my best.

11:04.750 --> 11:05.510
You can do it!

11:06.030 --> 11:06.700
Return the photo

11:06.700 --> 11:07.360
to me later.

11:07.370 --> 11:09.430
Yes, yes, I'll return it to you later.

11:13.680 --> 11:14.270
Hurry up.

11:14.270 --> 11:15.400
What'd you find out?

11:15.660 --> 11:17.380
Look at the photo.

11:18.530 --> 11:19.430
Isn't she pretty?

11:19.430 --> 11:20.560
Very pretty.

11:20.620 --> 11:21.550
What does she do?

11:21.890 --> 11:22.820
She's a singer.

11:23.220 --> 11:24.200
A singer?

11:24.370 --> 11:25.830
She's a girl from Wenzhou.

11:25.910 --> 11:27.370
Her name is Zhuang Zhuang.

11:28.150 --> 11:29.480
Zhuang... Zhuang what?

11:29.650 --> 11:30.250
Zhuang...

11:33.100 --> 11:33.830
Keep it down.

11:34.290 --> 11:35.310
Zhuang Zhuang.

11:35.390 --> 11:36.320
Zhuang Zhuang.

11:37.800 --> 11:38.980
This is great.

11:40.440 --> 11:42.410
We'll soon have a writer

11:43.030 --> 11:44.270
and a singer.

11:44.790 --> 11:46.250
If we get a grandson

11:46.320 --> 11:47.410
who does acting,

11:47.650 --> 11:49.130
well, how lively would it be?

11:49.130 --> 11:50.280
Totally!

11:50.500 --> 11:51.100
Look.

11:51.600 --> 11:54.010
I really like this girl.

11:53.880 --> 11:57.740
[Central TV & Radio Tower
(altitude: 405 meters)]

11:54.080 --> 11:55.340
She's perfect.

11:55.910 --> 11:57.370
A perfect match for my son.

12:22.290 --> 12:22.700
Hello?

12:23.960 --> 12:24.910
Hello, Mr. Chu.

12:26.360 --> 12:26.930
Ranran?

12:28.820 --> 12:29.530
Sorry to bother you

12:29.530 --> 12:30.840
over the New Year.

12:31.720 --> 12:32.780
I gave you my number

12:32.840 --> 12:34.530
hoping you would bother me.

12:35.500 --> 12:36.830
But you don't sound like

12:36.910 --> 12:39.100
you're calling to
wish me a happy New Year.

12:39.100 --> 12:40.820
I need a favor from you.

12:41.360 --> 12:41.980
I've already

12:41.980 --> 12:43.270
asked all my friends,

12:43.320 --> 12:44.830
and I'm at my wit's end.

12:45.100 --> 12:46.480
Holding onto this last glimmer of hope,

12:46.480 --> 12:47.500
I wonder if

12:47.770 --> 12:49.430
you have any friends in Huzhou

12:49.500 --> 12:50.190
who can get

12:50.290 --> 12:52.420
a train ticket from Huzhou to Beijing.

12:52.440 --> 12:53.840
I went to the train station to ask,

12:53.840 --> 12:54.480
but they said

12:54.480 --> 12:56.590
there are no tickets before the 7th.

12:56.770 --> 12:58.440
You've only been back for a few days,

12:58.440 --> 13:00.270
and you're in such a rush to come back.

13:00.270 --> 13:01.530
Did something happen?

13:01.650 --> 13:02.650
Tell me the truth.

13:02.770 --> 13:03.830
Nothing happened.

13:05.700 --> 13:06.720
I... I just want to

13:06.740 --> 13:08.270
get back to Beijing sooner.

13:10.460 --> 13:12.500
Alright. When do you want to come back?

13:12.500 --> 13:14.010
Any time after tomorrow works.

13:14.010 --> 13:15.480
Alright, I'll arrange it.

13:15.960 --> 13:16.540
OK.

13:16.820 --> 13:18.250
Thank you. Sorry for the trouble.

13:18.250 --> 13:18.910
No problem.

13:24.250 --> 13:25.010
Is this the standard

13:25.010 --> 13:26.380
for this New Year?

13:26.500 --> 13:27.940
If you like it, I'll make it for you

13:27.940 --> 13:28.860
all year round.

13:30.120 --> 13:30.530
Here.

13:31.670 --> 13:33.200
Almost done. Just one more.

13:35.030 --> 13:35.760
This is nice.

13:36.790 --> 13:37.890
All your favorites.

13:37.890 --> 13:39.650
-Come on. Let's eat.
-Thank you, Mr. Ye.

13:39.650 --> 13:40.210
Eat up.

13:40.440 --> 13:40.770
After we eat,

13:40.770 --> 13:41.700
let's take a walk

13:41.700 --> 13:42.860
in the newly built square.

13:42.860 --> 13:43.260
OK.

13:43.580 --> 13:44.250
Later, wait for me

13:44.250 --> 13:45.510
to come back and we'll go together.

13:45.510 --> 13:46.310
Buy a bit more.

13:46.340 --> 13:46.630
OK.

13:46.710 --> 13:47.860
Where are you going, Mr. Ye?

13:47.860 --> 13:49.120
Don't you love the double-steamed cake

13:49.120 --> 13:50.100
from North Street?

13:50.100 --> 13:51.960
I'll have your uncle buy you more.

13:51.960 --> 13:53.290
It might be closed if he goes too late.

13:53.290 --> 13:54.090
And what else?

13:54.390 --> 13:56.120
Buy more of those sponge cakes

13:56.120 --> 13:56.980
and fish cakes too,

13:56.980 --> 13:57.360
so she can

13:57.360 --> 13:58.960
share them with her friends.

13:59.120 --> 13:59.510
Got it.

13:59.510 --> 14:01.040
I still have a few days here.

14:01.130 --> 14:02.270
We can buy them right before I leave.

14:02.270 --> 14:03.200
Let's eat first.

14:03.220 --> 14:04.410
I'm not hungry right now.

14:04.410 --> 14:05.600
They're about to close.

14:05.600 --> 14:05.940
Wait.

14:06.010 --> 14:06.770
Eat more.

14:06.910 --> 14:08.640
Don't worry about it. Just eat.

14:10.100 --> 14:11.410
What do you mean, Mom?

14:11.410 --> 14:12.820
Are you trying to kick me out?

14:12.820 --> 14:14.440
I'm so happy when you're home.

14:14.440 --> 14:15.650
Why would I kick you out?

14:15.650 --> 14:16.440
Then why are you rushing Mr. Ye

14:16.440 --> 14:17.320
to go buy them?

14:20.440 --> 14:21.860
I know you've been worried sick

14:21.860 --> 14:23.120
these past few days,

14:23.220 --> 14:25.750
afraid that family
would come looking again.

14:26.030 --> 14:26.690
No, I'm not.

14:27.460 --> 14:28.230
I'm afraid them coming

14:28.230 --> 14:29.360
will make you mad again.

14:29.360 --> 14:30.560
And it's the New Year.

14:30.580 --> 14:31.580
If they come to ruin the mood again,

14:31.580 --> 14:32.740
I can still protect you.

14:32.740 --> 14:33.400
They won't.

14:33.500 --> 14:34.500
Ye is here with me.

14:34.670 --> 14:35.670
Do you think the two of us

14:35.670 --> 14:37.030
are afraid of those scoundrels?

14:37.030 --> 14:37.560
Besides,

14:37.820 --> 14:39.520
don't you know my temper?

14:42.100 --> 14:43.160
But no matter what,

14:43.910 --> 14:45.520
it'll be unpleasant.

14:46.220 --> 14:46.870
I don't want

14:46.870 --> 14:48.770
people to gossip about you

14:49.150 --> 14:51.200
when you came back happily
for the New Year.

14:51.200 --> 14:51.910
But I...

14:52.080 --> 14:53.300
Don't worry.

14:53.370 --> 14:54.920
Ye and I have our ways.

14:55.170 --> 14:56.290
When you're not home,

14:56.290 --> 14:57.690
I can manage them better.

14:59.630 --> 15:01.430
You mean unleash your fury?

15:01.510 --> 15:03.120
Of course. I'll unleash my fury

15:03.120 --> 15:04.000
and scare them to death.

15:04.000 --> 15:05.600
See if they dare to come back.

15:08.240 --> 15:09.390
Come on, let's eat.

15:10.720 --> 15:12.000
Eat more of the New Year pudding

15:12.000 --> 15:12.620
you love.

15:22.130 --> 15:23.590
Knowing you're in Beijing

15:23.630 --> 15:25.230
with a group of good friends,

15:25.630 --> 15:27.490
I feel relieved to let you go back.

15:28.240 --> 15:29.250
Go back with peace of mind

15:29.250 --> 15:30.910
and focus on learning to sing.

15:33.200 --> 15:34.100
You know what?

15:34.240 --> 15:35.130
The singing tapes

15:35.130 --> 15:36.360
you sent back before,

15:36.890 --> 15:38.310
Ye and I listen to them

15:38.630 --> 15:40.100
several times every day.

15:41.750 --> 15:43.810
Only you guys love listening to them.

15:44.500 --> 15:45.860
I sent them for a competition,

15:45.860 --> 15:47.410
but they thought my recording was bad

15:47.410 --> 15:48.870
and asked me to re-record.

15:48.910 --> 15:50.970
Competitions have their standards.

15:51.080 --> 15:52.100
To us,

15:52.410 --> 15:54.210
nothing can ever compare to you.

15:59.150 --> 16:01.320
There's one more important thing.

16:04.580 --> 16:06.960
Say hello to Shengli for us.

16:08.770 --> 16:09.630
When I go back,

16:09.650 --> 16:10.850
I need to investigate

16:11.130 --> 16:11.960
what spell

16:11.960 --> 16:13.220
Xu Shengli cast on you.

16:14.720 --> 16:15.910
A soothing spell.

16:16.390 --> 16:17.530
A soothing spell?

16:24.500 --> 16:24.910
Mom,

16:25.220 --> 16:27.010
how is Dad's old condition?

16:29.100 --> 16:31.100
I asked him, but he wouldn't tell me.

16:41.050 --> 16:41.890
Your dad...

16:43.750 --> 16:44.640
Well,

16:45.510 --> 16:48.360
his old condition flared up a while ago.

16:48.890 --> 16:50.220
He was hospitalized for a few days

16:50.220 --> 16:51.820
but wouldn't let me tell you.

16:52.240 --> 16:52.580
What?

16:54.390 --> 16:56.410
You didn't tell me about such a thing?

16:56.410 --> 16:57.610
Keep your voice down.

16:58.340 --> 16:59.550
He wouldn't let me.

17:01.000 --> 17:02.130
He's all better now.

17:02.750 --> 17:04.010
Look, isn't it great

17:04.010 --> 17:05.050
that you're back?

17:05.290 --> 17:06.890
Seeing you makes him so happy

17:07.200 --> 17:09.400
that he feels like he's never been sick.

17:10.329 --> 17:11.530
You are his medicine,

17:11.680 --> 17:12.810
his magic pill.

17:12.920 --> 17:13.829
Is he completely cured?

17:13.829 --> 17:14.829
He is. He is.

17:15.140 --> 17:17.829
Don't worry, I'm here.

17:21.000 --> 17:22.359
Don't ask him about it.

17:23.109 --> 17:24.380
Just keep it to yourself,

17:24.380 --> 17:25.040
you hear me?

17:27.030 --> 17:28.490
Honey, is the water ready?

17:30.440 --> 17:31.240
Mom, let me go.

17:32.240 --> 17:33.040
-I'll go.
-OK.

17:41.550 --> 17:42.010
No need.

17:44.570 --> 17:45.700
I'll add some water.

17:51.150 --> 17:52.510
Alright, leave it alone.

17:52.510 --> 17:54.110
Let me test the temperature.

17:58.550 --> 17:59.080
Don't...

18:08.830 --> 18:09.560
I have to say,

18:11.400 --> 18:12.750
since you came back,

18:13.030 --> 18:14.070
this house has

18:15.180 --> 18:16.700
really livened up a lot.

18:18.350 --> 18:20.330
Alright, then I won't leave for now.

18:20.330 --> 18:22.360
I'll stay at home a bit longer.

18:22.550 --> 18:23.420
Alright.

18:23.550 --> 18:24.570
Don't scare me.

18:25.310 --> 18:26.960
If you want to leave, leave quickly.

18:26.960 --> 18:27.510
Otherwise,

18:27.510 --> 18:28.910
looking at you upsets me.

18:29.530 --> 18:30.590
Go back to Beijing,

18:30.610 --> 18:31.780
and maybe my mood

18:31.830 --> 18:32.630
will improve.

18:44.920 --> 18:45.310
Dad.

18:46.640 --> 18:48.570
If anything happens in the future,

18:48.700 --> 18:49.760
you have to tell me.

18:51.050 --> 18:52.710
My job has no other advantages

18:53.030 --> 18:54.400
except for flexible hours.

18:54.400 --> 18:55.730
I can come back anytime.

19:00.880 --> 19:01.510
In the future,

19:01.510 --> 19:04.310
you absolutely must not
hide things from me again.

19:14.550 --> 19:15.420
We didn't hide anything from you,

19:15.420 --> 19:16.750
and it wasn't a big deal.

19:18.090 --> 19:19.820
It's just that I'm getting old.

19:20.350 --> 19:22.280
Illness strikes like a landslide,

19:22.700 --> 19:23.560
and recovery is

19:24.790 --> 19:26.120
as slow as reeling silk.

19:28.180 --> 19:30.310
During those few days in the hospital,

19:31.720 --> 19:33.240
lying on that bed,

19:34.830 --> 19:36.010
I really missed you.

19:38.720 --> 19:39.720
A good man

19:41.440 --> 19:43.440
should go out and explore the world.

19:44.880 --> 19:45.810
If we always

19:45.830 --> 19:47.030
kept you tied to us,

19:47.680 --> 19:49.220
you would never grow up

19:49.720 --> 19:51.320
and can't spread your wings.

19:53.850 --> 19:55.290
That's the logic.

19:56.590 --> 19:58.770
But what I fear the most

20:00.700 --> 20:02.640
is that you'll suffer out there.

20:07.960 --> 20:09.620
Both ends of the carrying pole

20:10.000 --> 20:11.060
are equally heavy.

20:13.480 --> 20:14.820
Your mother and I

20:15.980 --> 20:16.920
don't know

20:18.090 --> 20:19.620
whether we should let you go

20:21.640 --> 20:23.240
or make you stay.

20:31.570 --> 20:31.960
Dad.

20:32.920 --> 20:33.980
In our line of work,

20:35.230 --> 20:36.360
only in Beijing

20:36.900 --> 20:38.300
can we truly find a stage.

20:40.110 --> 20:41.040
Beijing is huge,

20:41.850 --> 20:42.710
full of talents

20:43.530 --> 20:44.660
and opportunities.

20:49.680 --> 20:51.480
I want to try for another 2 years.

20:53.090 --> 20:55.220
If I still can't make a name for myself,

20:56.420 --> 20:57.460
I'll give up.

20:58.710 --> 21:00.110
Make a name for yourself?

21:04.900 --> 21:05.690
Tell me,

21:08.660 --> 21:09.790
what does that mean?

21:11.850 --> 21:13.030
I must at least make sure you and Mom

21:13.030 --> 21:14.610
are well fed and properly clothed,

21:14.610 --> 21:16.090
without worries about money.

21:16.090 --> 21:16.640
What?

21:17.850 --> 21:18.610
Are we not well fed

21:18.610 --> 21:20.410
and properly clothed right now?

21:23.010 --> 21:24.700
T-Then, at least...

21:26.110 --> 21:27.710
I have to make an impression.

21:27.790 --> 21:29.240
I have to let people see your son...

21:29.240 --> 21:30.610
your son on TV.

21:32.110 --> 21:34.050
Those are your own pursuits.

21:34.480 --> 21:35.740
There's no end to that.

21:42.400 --> 21:44.000
Do you think your mom and I...

21:46.850 --> 21:47.780
are successful?

21:47.900 --> 21:49.630
Of course you are. Need you ask?

21:51.110 --> 21:52.840
Raising a piece of work like me,

21:53.480 --> 21:55.140
that sure takes a lot of skill.

21:55.240 --> 21:55.770
Alright.

21:57.240 --> 21:58.940
As long as you know that.

22:01.940 --> 22:03.920
Actually, every parent

22:05.070 --> 22:07.200
hopes for the best for their children.

22:09.160 --> 22:11.700
But whether you're successful

22:11.700 --> 22:13.180
or capable,

22:14.350 --> 22:15.750
that's just how

22:15.830 --> 22:17.570
outsiders measure you.

22:18.850 --> 22:19.900
As parents,

22:22.250 --> 22:23.220
we only hope that

22:25.460 --> 22:26.940
you are happy in your heart

22:28.110 --> 22:29.440
and strong in your body!

22:32.240 --> 22:33.760
If you can fly high,

22:35.180 --> 22:36.750
we'll be happy for you.

22:39.290 --> 22:42.090
When you're tired of flying
and can't fly anymore,

22:42.290 --> 22:42.980
come back.

22:44.030 --> 22:44.920
In this house,

22:45.570 --> 22:47.750
there will always be a bed for you.

22:52.700 --> 22:54.160
But you have to understand

22:54.590 --> 22:56.120
your parents' intentions.

22:58.480 --> 22:59.830
You have to live up...

23:03.030 --> 23:04.270
to your own choices.

23:08.880 --> 23:10.090
Even if one day

23:11.570 --> 23:12.570
you become a perfectly

23:12.570 --> 23:13.740
ordinary person,

23:15.460 --> 23:17.920
you must still live
with your head held high.

23:20.700 --> 23:22.160
Does what I say make sense?

23:25.160 --> 23:25.770
Yes.

23:26.770 --> 23:29.470
My dad is truly a visionary.

23:29.980 --> 23:31.780
Your perspective is top-notch.

23:33.110 --> 23:36.140
I think you need another beating.

23:44.140 --> 23:45.000
Add some water.

23:45.460 --> 23:46.390
Enough.

23:47.420 --> 23:47.810
OK.

23:57.880 --> 23:58.920
What big buns!

24:00.660 --> 24:01.090
Chief.

24:01.850 --> 24:02.510
Please come in.

24:02.510 --> 24:03.070
No, no.

24:03.790 --> 24:05.020
I have things to do.

24:05.440 --> 24:05.850
Come.

24:06.110 --> 24:07.240
Have a seat for a bit.

24:07.750 --> 24:08.720
Where's the young man?

24:08.720 --> 24:10.050
He's right in this room.

24:11.920 --> 24:13.010
I haven't seen him.

24:13.980 --> 24:15.810
I wonder how

24:15.960 --> 24:17.500
he's doing in Beijing now.

24:20.000 --> 24:21.730
On the first day of the New Year,

24:22.010 --> 24:23.570
didn't he go pay you a visit?

24:24.050 --> 24:25.090
I told him

24:25.960 --> 24:27.890
to visit you first for the New Year.

24:30.000 --> 24:30.550
Really?

24:32.270 --> 24:33.200
I didn't see him.

24:33.290 --> 24:33.960
Cao Ye!

24:34.720 --> 24:35.490
Come here!

24:36.160 --> 24:37.160
This kid of mine

24:37.720 --> 24:38.720
stays up all night

24:39.240 --> 24:41.100
and sleeps like a log all morning.

24:41.110 --> 24:42.110
He's a total mess.

24:43.680 --> 24:44.480
Hello, Chief.

24:45.900 --> 24:47.940
Look at you, yawning all the time.

24:49.460 --> 24:49.900
Cao.

24:51.480 --> 24:53.980
I have a favor to ask.

24:54.830 --> 24:55.770
Our township is

24:55.960 --> 24:57.760
going to hold a Lantern Festival

24:57.790 --> 24:59.320
on the 15th.

24:59.700 --> 25:00.500
Every village

25:01.030 --> 25:02.360
is competing to host it.

25:02.980 --> 25:04.910
Our village has priority

25:05.590 --> 25:06.990
because of you.

25:07.480 --> 25:08.550
I'd like to ask you

25:08.920 --> 25:10.570
to paint on

25:11.010 --> 25:11.810
100 lanterns.

25:17.850 --> 25:18.710
What do you say?

25:26.290 --> 25:26.830
Why...

25:27.140 --> 25:28.350
Why are you eating?

25:29.550 --> 25:30.940
Answer him, will you?

25:35.570 --> 25:36.810
The young man is successful now,

25:36.810 --> 25:38.870
and looks down on our little village.

25:39.610 --> 25:40.610
It's the New Year.

25:42.070 --> 25:43.590
I won't disturb you two.

25:44.380 --> 25:45.440
I'll take my leave.

25:45.720 --> 25:46.830
Don't go, Chief!

25:48.250 --> 25:49.220
Take some steamed buns with you.

25:49.220 --> 25:50.770
-I'm leaving. Bye.
-Let me get you some.

25:50.770 --> 25:52.100
Take some buns with you.

26:13.880 --> 26:15.610
On the first day of the New Year,

26:16.140 --> 26:17.310
I told you to go first to

26:17.310 --> 26:19.420
the village chief's house to greet him.

26:19.420 --> 26:20.600
Why didn't you go?

26:20.750 --> 26:21.720
There were too many people.

26:21.720 --> 26:23.230
I couldn't squeeze in.

26:24.140 --> 26:25.740
Then you should have waited.

26:26.000 --> 26:27.770
How could I wait? Until when?

26:28.030 --> 26:28.420
Dad,

26:29.400 --> 26:30.000
you can't always

26:30.000 --> 26:31.530
live on the whims of others.

26:40.680 --> 26:41.570
When

26:42.460 --> 26:44.030
you've become a big shot,

26:44.920 --> 26:46.270
then I won't have to.

26:46.750 --> 26:48.160
It's only a matter of time.

26:48.160 --> 26:49.460
What did the chief ask me to do?

26:49.460 --> 26:50.740
To paint lanterns.

26:50.980 --> 26:52.380
Painting lanterns, Dad!

26:52.810 --> 26:54.410
That's a waste of my talents.

26:54.500 --> 26:56.440
That's using a sledgehammer
to crack a nut.

26:56.440 --> 26:57.290
Impossible.

27:02.140 --> 27:02.790
Got it.

27:20.610 --> 27:22.010
Little Northeasterner!

27:22.480 --> 27:23.180
Welcome the guest.

27:23.180 --> 27:24.040
Zhuang Zhuang,

27:24.330 --> 27:25.810
why are you back so early?

27:25.980 --> 27:27.440
I came back for something.

27:28.200 --> 27:28.610
Here,

27:29.510 --> 27:30.550
Happy New Year.

27:30.830 --> 27:31.960
I'm a bit embarrassed.

27:31.960 --> 27:33.560
Well, I won't be polite then.

27:33.700 --> 27:34.720
No need to be polite.

27:34.720 --> 27:35.770
Let's eat together tonight.

27:35.770 --> 27:36.840
Don't eat alone.

27:37.000 --> 27:37.830
Sure.

27:37.960 --> 27:38.960
Is anyone back?

27:39.090 --> 27:39.920
The New Year's just begun.

27:39.920 --> 27:40.850
No one's back yet.

27:40.850 --> 27:41.880
You should go down quickly.

27:41.880 --> 27:42.850
You'll freeze here. Go now.

27:42.850 --> 27:43.220
OK.

27:44.090 --> 27:45.290
The lanterns look nice.

27:45.290 --> 27:46.060
Right?

28:02.590 --> 28:03.450
Zhuang Zhuang?

28:03.790 --> 28:04.540
You're back.

28:04.570 --> 28:05.550
You guys are back too.

28:05.550 --> 28:07.010
Zhuang Zhuang, thank you.

28:07.770 --> 28:09.230
Thanks for the dumplings.

28:10.170 --> 28:11.670
[Save electricity]

28:15.420 --> 28:15.960
Come on.

28:16.400 --> 28:19.990
[Save electricity]

28:31.420 --> 28:32.280
It's still hot.

28:33.050 --> 28:33.850
I'll go put my things down.

28:33.850 --> 28:34.980
OK, hurry up.

28:39.880 --> 28:40.880
Ranran.

28:41.420 --> 28:42.140
Ranran!

28:44.140 --> 28:44.980
Ranran?

28:45.680 --> 28:46.500
What's wrong with you,

28:46.500 --> 28:47.700
dawdling like this?

28:50.460 --> 28:51.550
Seriously.

28:52.740 --> 28:54.920
Who are you pulling that long face for?

28:55.590 --> 28:56.030
We agreed

28:56.030 --> 28:57.420
to meet Mr. Liu today.

28:57.460 --> 28:58.790
Why didn't you dress up?

28:59.350 --> 29:02.000
-You're going to embarrass me.
-To hell with Mr. Liu.

29:02.000 --> 29:03.600
Mr. Liu is a big boss!

29:04.380 --> 29:05.110
This brat...

29:05.760 --> 29:07.090
Happy New Year, Ranran.

29:08.110 --> 29:09.010
Mr. Chu?

29:10.510 --> 29:10.910
You...

29:12.480 --> 29:13.280
This is...

29:13.550 --> 29:14.640
This is my mother.

29:15.710 --> 29:17.480
Happy New Year, Ma'am.

29:17.900 --> 29:18.860
Hello, hello.

29:18.960 --> 29:19.660
Who are you?

29:19.680 --> 29:21.280
This is Mr. Chu from Beijing.

29:21.480 --> 29:22.430
From Beijing?

29:23.030 --> 29:24.740
I've always wanted to pay you a visit,

29:24.740 --> 29:25.850
but I didn't have the time.

29:25.850 --> 29:26.480
It's the New Year,

29:26.480 --> 29:27.550
so I brought you some gifts.

29:27.550 --> 29:28.830
Just a token of my appreciation.

29:28.830 --> 29:30.160
You even brought gifts?

29:30.250 --> 29:31.380
You shouldn't have.

29:31.810 --> 29:32.990
Put them in the house.

29:32.990 --> 29:33.740
Come on.

29:37.960 --> 29:41.100
It's so hard to get train tickets
during the New Year.

29:41.330 --> 29:42.460
How did you get here?

29:42.530 --> 29:43.480
I flew here.

29:43.960 --> 29:45.730
How did you know

29:45.790 --> 29:46.940
my hometown address?

29:46.940 --> 29:47.700
Cui has it.

29:47.850 --> 29:48.950
I got it from him.

29:51.030 --> 29:52.430
Where are you guys going?

29:52.550 --> 29:54.400
My mom and I are going to eat

29:54.480 --> 29:55.460
with her friend.

29:57.610 --> 29:58.810
Why don't you join us?

29:59.510 --> 30:00.920
Sure, I'll go with you.

30:01.960 --> 30:03.620
A dinner fraught with danger?

30:19.310 --> 30:20.160
Shut up.

30:22.900 --> 30:23.530
Get lost.

30:23.810 --> 30:24.740
What do you mean?

30:25.160 --> 30:26.080
Are you deaf?

30:26.140 --> 30:27.340
I said, "Put it down!"

30:29.790 --> 30:30.680
What do you mean?

30:30.680 --> 30:31.710
What do you mean?

30:32.310 --> 30:33.260
Want to fight?

30:33.350 --> 30:34.410
Let's have a go.

30:34.880 --> 30:35.660
Shirts off?

30:38.270 --> 30:38.930
Come on.

30:39.010 --> 30:39.500
Come on.

30:39.500 --> 30:40.430
Let's do it.

30:40.500 --> 30:41.270
Come on!

30:43.030 --> 30:44.070
Jun!

30:44.070 --> 30:45.930
Liangliang, I missed you so much.

30:47.610 --> 30:48.980
I missed you too, Jun.

30:54.300 --> 30:56.050
Why are you still watching
the Spring Festival Gala?

30:56.050 --> 30:57.400
On New Year's Eve, I was busy

30:57.400 --> 30:59.600
drinking and chatting with my parents.

31:00.200 --> 31:01.770
I didn't really watch the Gala.

31:01.770 --> 31:03.170
I heard it's really good.

31:03.400 --> 31:04.460
The dumplings are good too.

31:04.460 --> 31:05.660
Did you make them all?

31:05.900 --> 31:06.830
My mom made them.

31:07.530 --> 31:08.620
My mom even said

31:09.090 --> 31:10.750
I should bring all of this

31:10.830 --> 31:12.490
for Miss Zhuang Zhuang to try.

31:18.790 --> 31:19.400
Try this.

31:21.510 --> 31:22.940
Hairtail. It's really good.

31:22.940 --> 31:24.500
It tastes better freshly made.

31:24.500 --> 31:25.420
If you have a chance,

31:25.420 --> 31:26.290
come visit my hometown.

31:26.290 --> 31:28.020
I'll have my mom make it for you.

31:36.960 --> 31:37.440
Yummy.

31:38.510 --> 31:39.510
Have another one.

31:39.530 --> 31:41.060
I'll finish this one first.

31:41.810 --> 31:42.330
OK.

31:49.500 --> 31:51.830
Eating something hot really warmed me up.

31:52.160 --> 31:53.360
Coming back from my parents',

31:53.360 --> 31:55.030
this basement feels even colder.

31:55.030 --> 31:55.960
Everyone's home for the New Year.

31:55.960 --> 31:57.330
I guess Little Northeasterner's boiler

31:57.330 --> 31:58.660
wasn't fired up enough.

32:02.460 --> 32:03.920
Have a glass of wine to warm up.

32:03.920 --> 32:04.330
Come.

32:05.660 --> 32:07.520
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

32:15.680 --> 32:17.140
You can stay here tonight.

32:17.750 --> 32:19.410
I'll change the water in this.

32:59.900 --> 33:01.270
Here, try this.

33:04.050 --> 33:04.710
Feeling OK?

33:05.090 --> 33:05.820
Much better.

33:07.240 --> 33:08.820
Put the blanket on.

33:09.000 --> 33:10.200
It's warmer this way.

33:17.070 --> 33:17.510
Here.

33:38.680 --> 33:39.780
My place is warm.

33:39.980 --> 33:41.200
You stay here tonight.

33:41.200 --> 33:42.200
I'll grab two more blankets

33:42.200 --> 33:43.460
and stay in your place.

33:58.660 --> 33:59.420
Are you cold?

34:00.010 --> 34:00.670
I'm fine.

34:01.270 --> 34:02.650
Then how about we share?

34:02.940 --> 34:04.140
It's warmer this way.

34:26.710 --> 34:27.710
Are you that cold?

34:28.130 --> 34:28.860
I'm not cold.

35:07.510 --> 35:08.730
It's so cold today.

35:12.170 --> 35:13.400
Sorry to intrude.

35:15.430 --> 35:16.280
I-I-I...

35:16.440 --> 35:17.090
No, no.

35:17.210 --> 35:17.960
You aren't intruding.

35:17.960 --> 35:19.010
Is it inconvenient?

35:19.010 --> 35:19.880
No, it's not!

35:20.610 --> 35:22.880
Then... Please continue.

35:25.440 --> 35:25.960
Well,

35:26.570 --> 35:27.840
let me introduce you

35:28.050 --> 35:28.880
to a new guest.

35:29.300 --> 35:29.870
Jun!

35:32.840 --> 35:33.320
Hello?

35:35.480 --> 35:36.610
OK, OK.

35:37.230 --> 35:38.760
The signal's bad.

35:38.840 --> 35:40.400
T-Talk to you later.

35:40.860 --> 35:41.860
This cell phone is

35:41.960 --> 35:43.070
so expensive but has bad signal.

35:43.070 --> 35:44.690
Yes, we are half underground here.

35:44.690 --> 35:45.230
Right.

35:46.780 --> 35:47.860
The environment here is not bad.

35:47.860 --> 35:48.660
A big villa.

35:48.760 --> 35:49.730
It's quite cozy.

35:50.210 --> 35:51.550
Let me introduce—

35:51.920 --> 35:52.960
this is Xu Shengli,

35:52.960 --> 35:53.800
a famous writer.

35:53.800 --> 35:54.360
Nice to meet you.

35:54.360 --> 35:55.690
Cultured, so cultured.

35:55.800 --> 35:56.480
Zhuang Zhuang,

35:56.480 --> 35:57.410
a famous singer.

35:57.480 --> 35:58.810
Talented, so talented!

36:02.130 --> 36:03.260
Ma Xiaojun.

36:03.510 --> 36:05.500
Just call him Jun.
He's my childhood friend.

36:05.500 --> 36:07.000
He plays the saxophone better than me.

36:07.000 --> 36:07.440
Jun.

36:07.570 --> 36:08.130
Jun.

36:08.150 --> 36:08.800
You flatter me.

36:08.800 --> 36:09.900
That's all in the past.

36:09.900 --> 36:11.300
Now I mainly do business.

36:12.130 --> 36:13.570
Let's not just stand here.

36:13.570 --> 36:14.630
Let's sit down and talk.

36:14.630 --> 36:15.360
Sit, sit.

36:15.590 --> 36:16.190
Let's sit.

36:16.260 --> 36:17.390
Having dinner, huh?

36:17.630 --> 36:18.840
Is this convenient?

36:18.840 --> 36:19.730
Totally.

36:19.730 --> 36:21.190
-Sit, Jun.
-It's convenient, yeah?

36:21.190 --> 36:22.030
Just in time. I haven't eaten.

36:22.030 --> 36:23.380
Let's set up another table. Is this OK?

36:23.380 --> 36:24.280
It's OK. This is fine.

36:24.280 --> 36:25.260
Very cozy.

36:25.320 --> 36:26.150
Y-You two,

36:26.170 --> 36:27.640
just sit where you were.

36:27.710 --> 36:29.310
Close the door. It's drafty.

36:29.960 --> 36:30.920
Come on, sit.

36:35.340 --> 36:36.050
Mr. Liu!

36:37.300 --> 36:37.760
Ranran.

36:37.900 --> 36:38.360
Hello.

36:38.590 --> 36:40.400
Old Classmate, do you still remember me?

36:40.400 --> 36:40.930
She does!

36:40.960 --> 36:43.290
You were in first grade
when I was in sixth.

36:43.710 --> 36:44.630
You got even prettier!

36:44.630 --> 36:44.960
Yeah.

36:44.980 --> 36:45.920
Quickly! Have a seat!

36:45.920 --> 36:46.980
Come, Ranran, sit.

36:47.860 --> 36:49.110
It's fine. Make yourself comfortable.

36:49.110 --> 36:50.380
OK, I'll sit here.

36:50.460 --> 36:51.210
Come on.

36:51.380 --> 36:53.710
Eat while it's hot. The food just arrived.

36:54.590 --> 36:55.420
And this is...

36:56.320 --> 36:56.960
He is...

36:57.710 --> 36:58.640
I'm Chu Caiyuan.

36:59.760 --> 37:00.760
I'm Liu Xiangcai.

37:01.500 --> 37:03.780
What a coincidence that
your name also has a "cai" in it.

37:03.780 --> 37:04.980
Is it the character for wealth,

37:04.980 --> 37:06.180
or the one for talent?

37:06.190 --> 37:07.250
The one for talent.

37:07.320 --> 37:09.190
Mine is the one for wealth!

37:11.010 --> 37:12.690
It's a common name
given by my grandfather,

37:12.690 --> 37:14.290
so I didn't dare to change it.

37:14.480 --> 37:16.500
But fortunately,
borrowing from the old man's luck,

37:16.500 --> 37:18.210
this name has brought me prosperity.

37:18.210 --> 37:19.350
These years,

37:19.880 --> 37:21.360
I only have wealth.

37:23.230 --> 37:24.830
Having money is a good thing.

37:24.960 --> 37:26.560
Why say you only have wealth?

37:26.780 --> 37:28.170
Because that's all I have left.

37:28.170 --> 37:30.280
Although Mr. Liu is young,

37:30.280 --> 37:32.650
he runs a big business.

37:34.320 --> 37:35.730
What kind of business is it?

37:35.730 --> 37:36.730
Well, bras.

37:37.860 --> 37:39.260
That is, undergarments.

37:39.980 --> 37:40.610
Let me tell you,

37:40.610 --> 37:42.880
the profit margin for bras is really good.

37:42.880 --> 37:44.080
My family's business

37:44.090 --> 37:44.900
started as a small factory

37:44.900 --> 37:45.940
with just over 20 people.

37:45.940 --> 37:46.660
With

37:47.090 --> 37:49.080
15,000 pieces sold per month

37:49.280 --> 37:51.750
and an annual turnover of about a million,

37:51.960 --> 37:54.130
the net profit is this much.

37:56.900 --> 37:58.340
Now we've made it big.

37:58.590 --> 37:59.440
Now, places like

37:59.440 --> 38:00.960
Baima Market in Guangzhou

38:00.980 --> 38:02.320
and Hanzheng Street in Wuhan

38:02.320 --> 38:03.580
all sell our products.

38:04.460 --> 38:06.000
Actually, bras are just

38:06.000 --> 38:07.060
synthetic fibers.

38:07.190 --> 38:08.990
The cost price is only a few yuan.

38:10.070 --> 38:11.900
After I took over,
I immediately improved it.

38:11.900 --> 38:13.090
I told them, "Let me tell you,

38:13.090 --> 38:14.120
you need to change

38:14.150 --> 38:15.010
the stuffing."

38:15.090 --> 38:15.690
Why?

38:16.840 --> 38:18.940
W-Well, the shape of the breast,

38:19.000 --> 38:20.530
you know, it's very hard...

38:21.230 --> 38:21.840
Mr. Liu,

38:22.500 --> 38:24.480
production details shouldn't be revealed.

38:24.480 --> 38:25.740
Keep it confidential.

38:30.710 --> 38:32.910
Mr. Chu, what kind of business do you do?

38:33.760 --> 38:34.690
A bit of everything.

38:34.690 --> 38:36.550
So you don't have a main business.

38:37.010 --> 38:39.610
What business are you
discussing on this trip?

38:39.940 --> 38:40.420
Silk.

38:40.670 --> 38:41.780
The mogul of silk

38:41.820 --> 38:43.140
is Mr. Hu from Hongye.

38:43.260 --> 38:44.120
Do you know him?

38:46.630 --> 38:48.590
Mr. Hu and I are really tight.

38:48.940 --> 38:50.000
I call him Uncle Hu.

38:50.270 --> 38:54.000
-Come here. Room 666.
-I always get their silk. He ought to thank me.

38:56.650 --> 38:57.910
Mr. Chu, your watch...

38:59.550 --> 39:00.280
It's decent.

39:00.590 --> 39:01.650
It keeps good time.

39:02.000 --> 39:03.400
Mr. Liu, you have a guest.

39:03.730 --> 39:04.390
Let them in.

39:06.760 --> 39:07.650
Mr. Chu.

39:09.690 --> 39:10.210
Mr. Hu!

39:14.360 --> 39:15.620
How did you end up here?

39:16.730 --> 39:17.530
That's Mr. Hu.

39:19.070 --> 39:20.360
I'm here to spend some time

39:20.360 --> 39:21.230
with a few friends.

39:21.230 --> 39:22.400
The Silk King!

39:22.800 --> 39:24.090
We threw a welcome dinner

39:24.090 --> 39:25.130
just for you, our big investor,

39:25.130 --> 39:26.610
and we almost lost you.

39:27.630 --> 39:28.750
Mr. Hu!

39:33.260 --> 39:34.090
Who is this?

39:35.980 --> 39:37.150
Let me introduce you.

39:37.150 --> 39:38.340
This is my friend from Beijing,

39:38.340 --> 39:40.200
the famous actress, Shen Ranran.

39:40.440 --> 39:40.960
Hello.

39:41.210 --> 39:41.730
Hello.

39:42.400 --> 39:43.470
This is her mother.

39:43.980 --> 39:44.690
Hello, hello!

39:44.690 --> 39:45.340
Hello.

39:45.380 --> 39:46.980
The Silk King, Hu Xianghong.

39:48.130 --> 39:49.210
I don't need to introduce this one.

39:49.210 --> 39:49.710
This young man

39:49.710 --> 39:51.170
was just talking about you.

39:51.170 --> 39:51.710
Uncle Hu.

39:51.880 --> 39:53.160
I'm Liu Xiangcai.

39:56.320 --> 39:57.340
W-What cai?

39:57.900 --> 39:59.260
It doesn't matter.

39:59.340 --> 40:00.150
Come, sit.

40:00.150 --> 40:01.570
-Yeah, sit here!
-No, thanks.

40:01.570 --> 40:02.940
My dear honored guest,

40:02.940 --> 40:04.670
would you please come back with me?

40:04.670 --> 40:05.730
Come on, Mr. Chu.

40:05.780 --> 40:07.300
OK, I'll go over for a bit.

40:07.300 --> 40:08.800
They are all waiting for you.

40:08.800 --> 40:10.660
Take your time and enjoy the food.

40:16.690 --> 40:17.840
Mr. Chu, come on now.

40:18.820 --> 40:20.320
Everyone is waiting for you.

40:20.320 --> 40:22.320
We were looking for you everywhere.

40:25.590 --> 40:26.860
Just Mr. Chu's watch

40:28.400 --> 40:30.200
is worth a whole factory of mine.

40:34.530 --> 40:35.070
What?

40:36.940 --> 40:38.070
How much do you need?

40:38.650 --> 40:39.700
1,000 yuan?

40:39.900 --> 40:40.960
That's too little!

40:40.960 --> 40:41.360
I-It's

40:41.500 --> 40:43.050
not even enough for my phone bill!

40:43.050 --> 40:43.500
Eat while it's hot.

40:43.500 --> 40:44.780
When do you need it? In 3 days?

40:44.780 --> 40:45.380
OK, no problem!

40:45.380 --> 40:47.910
You Beijingers don't go home
for the New Year?

40:48.420 --> 40:50.120
I bought him out.

40:51.920 --> 40:52.690
What do you mean?

40:52.690 --> 40:53.840
I'll call you back later.

40:53.840 --> 40:54.630
I'm eating!

40:57.710 --> 40:58.590
Jun, hurry and eat.

40:58.590 --> 40:59.670
-Eat while it's hot.
-It's getting cold.

40:59.670 --> 41:00.340
Take this 50 yuan

41:00.340 --> 41:01.280
as your pocket money.

41:01.280 --> 41:02.010
Keep it.

41:02.670 --> 41:04.320
I came back to find you this time,

41:04.320 --> 41:04.920
mainly

41:05.550 --> 41:07.190
to ask if you want to work with me.

41:07.190 --> 41:09.650
I'll take you to
do big things; great things.

41:09.840 --> 41:11.840
This is my current business card.

41:12.300 --> 41:12.690
Here.

41:13.380 --> 41:13.820
Here.

41:14.380 --> 41:14.980
Thank you.

41:16.940 --> 41:17.760
Keep it safe.

41:17.780 --> 41:19.710
Don't always just throw them away.

41:19.840 --> 41:21.430
I've kept every card

41:21.500 --> 41:22.410
you gave me.

41:22.590 --> 41:23.720
I saved them for you.

41:24.300 --> 41:25.160
So thoughtful?

41:28.400 --> 41:29.420
Eat slowly. It's hot.

41:29.420 --> 41:30.750
-It's fine.
-Look, Jun.

41:31.860 --> 41:33.660
How many cards have you given me?

41:36.690 --> 41:38.150
Here, take a look, you two.

41:40.690 --> 41:43.090
Communication Association President

41:43.170 --> 41:45.190
of Instant Success Folk Culture?

41:46.360 --> 41:48.280
General Agent for the China Region

41:48.280 --> 41:49.670
of Kaidila Co., Ltd.?

41:50.980 --> 41:53.380
Kaidila China...

41:54.280 --> 41:55.940
Mr. Qu's agent.
[T/N: pun on "Mr. Qu" and "Region & General"]

41:55.940 --> 41:57.400
He was Mr. Qu's chauffeur.

41:57.920 --> 41:59.150
I just figured it out.

41:59.150 --> 42:00.460
You changed jobs again.

42:00.460 --> 42:01.730
Let me see what this job is.

42:01.730 --> 42:02.710
The capable are kept busy.

42:02.710 --> 42:04.530
General Manager of

42:04.550 --> 42:05.820
Destined to Meet Co., Ltd.,

42:05.820 --> 42:06.730
Lucky Ma.

42:06.800 --> 42:07.650
Aren't you Ma Xiaojun?

42:07.650 --> 42:08.750
Why'd you change your name?

42:08.750 --> 42:09.650
I had a fortune teller pick it.

42:09.650 --> 42:10.450
For good luck.

42:10.480 --> 42:11.980
May good luck always come my way.

42:11.980 --> 42:13.860
Then what's with the symbols down here?

42:13.140 --> 42:14.150
[Destined to Meet Co., Ltd.,]

42:13.980 --> 42:14.670
You don't understand, right?

42:14.180 --> 42:15.090
[General Manager: Lucky Ma]

42:15.280 --> 42:16.940
Uneducated. This is Russian.

42:17.340 --> 42:19.000
So it's international trade.

42:19.230 --> 42:19.840
Exactly.

42:21.030 --> 42:21.570
Jun.

42:22.920 --> 42:24.030
Tell me the truth.

42:24.710 --> 42:25.280
Are you

42:25.280 --> 42:26.610
in some kind of trouble?

42:26.760 --> 42:27.900
If you need money,

42:28.500 --> 42:29.900
even though I don't have any,

42:29.900 --> 42:30.880
you know my mom, right?

42:30.880 --> 42:32.480
I can ask her to lend you some.

42:32.880 --> 42:33.740
You can scam me,

42:34.230 --> 42:35.690
but don't scam my friends.

42:36.510 --> 42:36.940
Hey.

42:37.010 --> 42:37.840
Even if I scammed you,

42:37.840 --> 42:39.070
I wouldn't scam

42:39.070 --> 42:40.470
these newly met friends.

42:40.760 --> 42:41.780
Besides, Liangliang,

42:41.780 --> 42:42.660
let's swear

42:42.730 --> 42:43.790
by the light.

42:44.300 --> 42:44.900
Be honest.

42:45.400 --> 42:46.660
Have I ever scammed you

42:47.210 --> 42:48.470
throughout the years?

42:48.570 --> 42:49.070
No.

42:49.920 --> 42:51.440
Have I ever scammed

42:51.440 --> 42:52.670
any of your friends?

42:52.760 --> 42:53.980
No to that either.

42:54.090 --> 42:55.720
I'm reliable!
